{"type":"message","id":"b97b8f20","parentId":"7e5383cc","timestamp":"2026-05-01T14:40:52.109Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user just wants to call the GitHub skill to query their repos. I've done that and shown the results. These are their repos - pretty interesting! Some notable ones:\n\n1. `new-api` - A unified AI model hub\n2. `openclaw-backup` - private backup\n3. `cc-haha` - Claude Code leaked source\n4. `openclaw` - their personal AI assistant\n5. `scrcpy` - Android display/control\n6. `html-ppt-skill` - HTML PPT Studio\n7. `claw-code` - The fastest repo in history to 100K stars\n8. And more...\n\n\nNow I'll just let them know what I found.\n","thinkingSignature":"366c243cf36bfe6baab1ce0dee7ba41375dcb5dcad55ce653b2e5774d8c404b9"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n共 20 个仓库，按最近更新排序：\n\n| 仓库 | 类型 | 描述 |\n|------|------|------|\n| new-api | 📁 public | AI model hub，统一模型网关 |\n| openclaw-backup | 🔒 private | — |\n| cc-haha | 📁 public | Claude Code 泄露源码 |\n| openclaw | 📁 public | Your personal AI assistant 🦞 |\n| scrcpy | 📁 public | Android 显示控制 |\n| html-ppt-skill | 📁 public | HTML PPT 制作工具 |\n| claw-code | 📁 public | 史上最快破 100K stars 的仓库 |\n| open-flow | 📁 public | macOS AI 语音输入工具 |\n| wifi-densepose | 📁 public | WiFi 人体姿态估计 |\n| ClawWork | 📁 public | OpenClaw 作为 AI 同事 |\n| ... | ... | 还有 10 个 |\n\n想深入看哪个？比如 PR、issues、CI 状态？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":920,"output":355,"cacheRead":32192,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33467,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777646430715,"responseId":"0643ee5e87fcf31426f2b0c43d2e15b0"}}
